187
00:27:27,789 --> 00:27:29,915
- You're under arrest.
- What?

188
00:27:30,083 --> 00:27:33,126
Anything you say can and will be
used against you in a court of law.

189
00:27:33,294 --> 00:27:36,088
I don't think you understand.
There's something weird going on.

190
00:27:36,255 --> 00:27:37,798
My daughter, she's in danger.

191
00:27:37,965 --> 00:27:40,134
