202
00:28:16,548 --> 00:28:18,340
You're going back to the station.

203
00:28:18,508 --> 00:28:20,676
- Are you kidding?
- Nope.

204
00:28:21,469 --> 00:28:23,178
Have you heard
a single word I've said?

205
00:28:23,346 --> 00:28:24,972
- Yeah, I hear you.
- Have you heard...

206
00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:26,682
