anyone's come under any harm.

226
00:29:46,474 --> 00:29:48,308
- Good Christ.
- Now, you mind telling me...

227
00:29:48,476 --> 00:29:50,477
...what your wife's doing
up here, Mr...?

228
00:29:50,645 --> 00:29:52,771
- Da Silva, Chris Da Silva.
- My pleasure, Chris...

229
00:29:52,939 --> 00:29:55,649
