to Silent Hill.

236
00:30:10,624 --> 00:30:12,250
- Let's take a look around.
- Yes, sir.

237
00:30:12,417 --> 00:30:14,293
While Chris here tells me
what's going on.

238
00:30:16,338 --> 00:30:19,006
She disappeared yesterday.
I spoke to her...

239
00:30:19,174 --> 00:30:20,883
...when she stopped for gas
in Brahams.

240
00:30:21,552 --> 00:30:23,970
