off me?

255
00:31:42,052 --> 00:31:44,512
No. Get walking.

256
00:31:44,680 --> 00:31:47,349
There's a fire-lookout tower
on the far side of Toluca Lake.

257
00:31:47,516 --> 00:31:50,268
