- The police records.

371
00:55:26,527 --> 00:55:29,028
Sorry, sir,
those records are confidential.

372
00:55:29,196 --> 00:55:31,365
No, no, I can't...
No, listen, I...

373
00:55:31,533 --> 00:55:33,784
Sorry, sir,
I can't access that information.

374
00:55:33,952 --> 00:55:35,452
- Listen, goddamn it.
- Sir.

375
00:55:35,620 --> 00:55:37,037
- This is an emergency.
- I can't...

376
00:55:37,205 --> 00:55:39,248
I can't help you.

377
00:55:55,473 --> 00:55:58,225
They used to say
this place was haunted.

378
00:55:58,810 --> 00:56:00,936
I think they were right.

379
00:56:10,363 --> 00:56:12,990
Help! No!

380
00:56:13,158 --> 00:56:15,033
- Stay away.
- Come on.

381
00:56:15,201 --> 00:56:18,121
Stay away, sinner.

382
00:56:18,289 --> 00:56:19,664
Get back!

383
00:56:19,832 --> 00:56:21,666
Hey.

384
00:56:21,834 --> 00:56:23,586
It's here.

385
00:56:25,380 --> 00:56:27,590
Faith is our destroyer.
Faith has brought us doom.

386
