Who was that?

397
00:56:54,826 --> 00:56:57,953
- I've seen her before.
- Dahlia was cast out.

398
00:56:58,121 --> 00:57:00,206
Not even the darkness wants her.

399
00:57:00,373 --> 00:57:03,000
- She's lost her daughter too.
- What?

400
00:57:03,168 --> 00:57:08,547
- Sinners deserve to lose their spawn.
- What are you doing here, Anna?

401
00:57:10,300 --> 00:57:12,885
Mother needs more food.

402
00:57:13,470 --> 00:57:15,096
You mean there are
other people here?

403
00:57:18,185 --> 00:57:20,186
