404
00:57:20,354 --> 00:57:22,813
- Anna.
- We take refuge in the church.

405
00:57:23,315 --> 00:57:26,234
Anna, listen to me.

406
00:57:26,777 --> 00:57:29,195
I've lost my daughter.
She's all alone.

407
00:57:29,488 --> 00:57:32,198
Can you imagine how frightened
she must feel?

408
00:57:32,366 --> 00:57:34,367
Tell me, have you seen her?

409
00:57:34,534 --> 00:57:35,952
Do you know where she is?

410
00:57:39,706 --> 00:57:42,667
If she has faith, she might survive.

411
00:57:42,834 --> 00:57:43,834
If not...

412
00:57:46,838 --> 00:57:47,922
I'm taking this.

413
00:57:50,217 --> 00:57:51,968
Have you seen this?

414
00:57:52,511 --> 00:57:54,804
I've seen it at the school.

415
00:57:55,347 --> 00:57:59,183
It's on all the buildings
the elders of my elders built.

416
00:57:59,351 --> 00:58:03,854
It's a symbol of our unity,
a symbol of our faith.

417
00:58:15,244 --> 00:58:16,953
Rose, look at this.

418
00:58:19,039 --> 00:58:22,208
- What is it?
- Just like yours.

419
00:58:23,585 --> 00:58:27,046
- Where did you find it?
- They're all over the floor.

420
00:58:41,312 --> 00:58:42,562
Rose.

421
00:58:43,272 --> 00:58:44,897
Check this out.

422
00:58:46,734 --> 00:58:50,862
